The Fund Class I (AVALX) and Class A (AVFAX) shares have an annualized gross expense ratio of 1.50% and 1.76%, respectively. The Fund Class I (AVALX) and Class A (AVFAX)'s net annualized expense ratio, after fee waiver, is 1.50%, and 1.75%, respectively. Under the waiver, the Advisor has contractually agreed to limit certain fees and/or reimburse certain of the Fund 's expenses through April 30, 2018.
