Open Architecture Platform
For advisors who are seeking the flexibility of an independent firm, but the strength of a wire house, Aegis Capital bridges the best of both worlds. Ae...

Open Architecture Platform
For advisors who are seeking the flexibility of an independent firm, but the strength of a wire house, Aegis Capital bridges the best of both worlds. Aegis is one of the few firms in the industry that maintains a multi-clearing platform through RBC and APEX. Aegis provides a full-service platform along with a conflict-free atmosphere. Our open architectural model allows advisors to put their clients first by offering a full array of products while, at the same time, not being tied to any proprietary offerings. Whether your business is Wealth Management, Individual Equities, Bonds, Insurance, Annuities or anything in-between, Aegis Capital has been running a full-service investment shop for the past 26 years.



