Our Story - Aegis Capital Corp.



























        Client Login           AEGIS CAPITAL CORP A Regional Financial Services Company that makes a difference.  Changing the way business is done one person at a time.       






Our Story


Our Story
Aegis Capital Corporation was founded in 1984 by Robert Eide, the Current CEO and Chairman. Aegis’ origins are based on servicing the specific needs of an extremely affluent customer base specializing in complex real estate transactions. As the needs of our clients broadened, so did our product base, and today we have become a premiere full service East Coast Regional Investment Firm with locations stretching from Florida to New York.
Aegis is able to bring quality service through its clearing relationships with RBC Correspondent Services (RBC CS), a division of RBC Capital Markets, LLC. Apex Clearing Corporation. Our clients value the safety of knowing their assets are held at third-party custodians. Our management team serves on the boards of NYSE, AMEX, and NASDAQ companies, so we have the practical experience on the challenges facing today’s industry leaders. Whether a client is looking for wealth management products or institutional services, Aegis has the team to assist. We pride ourselves on being able to provide the attention that our diverse client base expects.
Aegis continues to stay true to its roots, offering our clients the capabilities of any large bank, with the quality and service of your local banker.








Founded in 1984, Aegis Capital Corp. is a full service retail and institutional broker-dealer located in New York City. Our management is committed to providing the highest level of service to our clients. 

