Managing risk backed by strength, long-term stability and insurance innovation.









Welcome to Aegis Security Insurance Company
Aegis Security Insurance Company is an “A” rated insurer by A.M. Best (Financial Size VII) and is licensed in all 50 states and the District of Columbia. Our principal focus is specialty Property and Casualty insurance, Surety and Accident and Health insurance. We distribute our products through a nationwide network of independent agencies. Our commitment to our Managing General Agent and independent agency partners is underscored by our 37-year history of profitable growth.









ExperiencedTalent
An industry-leading team with unmatched expertise in our core product lines is behind the success of Aegis Security. Management discipline, local expertise, responsiveness, ease of doing business and long-term relationships are the hallmarks that separate us in the marketplace.



UnderwritingIntegrity
Our strict underwriting guidelines, pricing model, rate adjustments and catastrophe containment measures allow us to continue to deliver profitable business for our company, partners and investors.



NicheProducts
Our focus is on niche segments and hard-to-place risks. We bring a level of specialization to our MGA partners and their agents and producers we believe is unique to the market we serve.



Specialty ClaimsExpertise
Our seasoned CAT team of preferred licensed adjusters and appraisers allows us to respond quickly when it matters most. We’re able to issue payments on the scene, and are prepared to settle claims in the fastest, most efficient way possible.







Aegis Security has historically produced operating earnings through consistent underwriting discipline, adequate and fair rates and conservative investment practices. Innovation and the leveraging of advanced technology is also key to our future success. We have developed a web-based rating system centered on our customer needs. We also employ advanced tools and technology to provide efficient and effective claims resolution. All of this is backed by our high caliber team of CAT-preferred adjusters working hard to get people back on their feet and into their homes when disaster strikes.





Trust the strength, stability, knowledge and responsiveness of Aegis Security.
Learn more about us, our management team and insurance products and how we can best serve you. Contact us at (855) 790-0550.
 



